&apos;micaela.lumpkin@cvest.com;behnam.hoss@cvest.com&apos;</formula>
    </fieldOverrides>
    <fieldOverrides>
        <field>HtmlBody</field>
        <formula>&apos;Hello &apos; +  Opportunity.Contact__r.FirstName  + &apos;,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thank you for choosing CoreVest for your term financing. We would like to set up a kick off call for your transaction &apos; +  Opportunity.Name  + &apos;, so we can discuss your deal, establish timing and you can meet your underwriting team. &amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;Please advise which time works best.&amp;nbsp; Please note that times are Pacific.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;10:00 am PST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;11:00 am PST&lt;br /&gt;12:00 pm &amp;nbsp;PST&lt;br /&gt;Once you have selected a time, I will send a conference call invitation with dial-in information. If you would like another team member on your end to join, I will gladly include them, so please provide their contact information.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thank you,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;**Please make sure to include anyone that will be assisting you (i.e. property manager/legal counsel etc.)&lt;br /&gt;&apos;</formula>
    </fieldOverrides>
    <fieldOverrides>
        <field>Subject</field>
        <formula>&apos;Kick Off Email - &apos; + Opportunity.Name</formula>
    </fieldOverrides>
    <fieldOverrides>
        <field>ToAddress</field>
        <formula>Opportunity.Contact__r.Email</formula>
    </fieldOverrides>
